<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.6">
<l>matucūtaṉai yaṉṟi maṟṟilēṉeṉ ṟettāluṅ karumamiṉṟi</l>
<l>tuticūḻnta pāṭalkaḷ pāṭiyāṭa niṉṟūḻi yūḻitoṟu</l>
<l>metircūḻal pukkeṉait tōrpiṟappu meṉakkē yaruḷkaḷceyya</l>
<l>viticūḻnta tāleṉak kēlammāṉ tirivik kiramaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing aeon after aeon while [I] danced [and] sang songs that intented praise,</l>
<l>without any(?) action, saying “I am without any other than Madhusūdana”,</l>
<l>entering future incarnations while [he] did graces to me through one entire birth,</l>
<l>if it it for me (eṉakkēl?), there is considering the father Trivikrama as [my] fate.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
